<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM3.2.7">
<l>eññāṉṟu nāmirun tiruntiraṅki neñcē</l>
<l>meyñāṉa miṉṟi viṉaiyiyal piṟappaḻunti</l>
<l>yeññāṉṟu meṅku moḻivaṟa niṟaintuniṉṟa</l>
<l>meyñāṉac cōtik kaṇṇaṉai mēvutumē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>We, forever existing [and] existing, lamenting, o heart,</l>
<l>without true knowledge, being pressed into birth of karmic nature,</l>
<l>shall be attached to Kṛṣṇa, the light of true knowledge</l>
<l>who stands endlessly full every time and everywhere.</l> 
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
